sqlQuery: SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, MIN(checking.targetID) as agg_1 FROM savingAccount JOIN customer ON savingAccount.userID = customer.custID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.targetID JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.targetID JOIN company ON customer.companyID = company.companyID JOIN loanapps ON customer.custID = loanapps.applicantID JOIN loantrans ON customer.custID = loantrans.applicantID JOIN checkingAccount ON customer.custID = checkingAccount.userID  WHERE transfer.type IN ('donate', 'service', 'transfer', 'salary', 'invest') AND (customer.gender = 'male' OR (customer.gender = 'male' AND customer.gender LIKE '%m%ale%')) AND customer.checking_credit >= 0.0 AND (customer.name = 'Bai Xinyang' OR (customer.age <= 27.937824116404194 AND customer.name IN ('Liu Jing', 'Cai Bo', 'Zhou Xiuzhen', 'Cai Ping', 'Lin Yize', 'Yang Min', 'He Yutong', 'Yu Yimo', 'Fu Yutong', 'Zhu Dan'))) AND customer.city LIKE '%Shanghai%' LIMIT 1000;

SELECT SUM(customer.age + company.checking_credit) as agg_0 FROM company JOIN customer ON company.companyID = customer.companyID JOIN loantrans ON customer.custID = loantrans.applicantID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.sourceID JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.targetID JOIN loanapps ON loantrans.appID = loanapps.id  WHERE transfer.type IN ('invest', 'donate', 'service', 'red_packet', 'business', 'transfer', 'salary') AND transfer.type NOT LIKE '%transf%er%' AND loanapps.id <= 436670.29202407436 AND transfer.targetID >= 91614.45626683123 AND company.loan_balance >= 1000000.0 AND loantrans.duration <= 365.0 AND checking.id <= 234013.6916060721 AND company.province LIKE '%L%iaoning%' AND (checking.sourceID >= 301543.62372759444 OR (checking.sourceID >= 301694.72620686254 AND checking.sourceID >= 301577.99359762523)) AND customer.city = 'Hami';

SELECT MIN(company.loan_balance) as agg_0 FROM company JOIN customer ON company.companyID = customer.companyID JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.sourceID  WHERE customer.saving_credit >= 0.0 AND (customer.name IN ('Xu Yimo', 'Xiao Xinning', 'Mao Juan', 'Cao Bo', 'Tang Pengfei', 'Duan Ling', 'Fu Fang', 'Qin Xiulan') OR customer.name = 'Kong Lanying');

SELECT company.city, checking.type, company.name, MAX(checking.amount) as agg_0, SUM(checking.sourceID) as agg_1, MIN(loanapps.amount + loantrans.id) as agg_2 FROM checkingAccount JOIN customer ON checkingAccount.userID = customer.custID JOIN loantrans ON customer.custID = loantrans.applicantID JOIN loanapps ON loantrans.appID = loanapps.id JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.targetID JOIN savingAccount ON customer.custID = savingAccount.userID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.sourceID JOIN company ON customer.companyID = company.companyID  WHERE loanapps.status IN ('under_review') AND loanapps.status IN ('under_review') AND company.category NOT LIKE '%mining_au%xiliary%' AND (transfer.type IN ('invest', 'business') OR transfer.targetID <= 212438.08639036794 OR transfer.type LIKE '%d%onate%') AND loanapps.loanapps_ts LIKE '%2%023-10-19%' AND transfer.type != 'transfer' AND loantrans.status LIKE '%under_review%' AND savingAccount.balance <= 2000.0 AND savingAccount.userID >= 61886.255063138 AND company.province IN ('Inner_Mongolia') AND checkingAccount.Isblocked <= 0.0 AND checking.amount <= 20.644207400797725 GROUP BY company.city, checking.type, company.name ORDER BY company.city, checking.type, company.name LIMIT 1000;

SELECT customer.gender, company.last_update_timestamp, company.category, MIN(checkingAccount.accountID + customer.age) as agg_0 FROM transfer JOIN customer ON transfer.targetID = customer.custID JOIN checkingAccount ON customer.custID = checkingAccount.userID JOIN savingAccount ON customer.custID = savingAccount.userID JOIN company ON customer.companyID = company.companyID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.targetID  WHERE (transfer.type IN ('red_packet', 'donate', 'service', 'business', 'invest') OR transfer.targetID <= 123939.71966888352 OR transfer.type LIKE '%d%onate%') AND customer.name IN ('Lu Deming', 'Ren Bo', 'Shen Yuxing', 'Zhang Yuxing', 'Fang Deming', 'Tang Jianguo', 'Kong Zhiming', 'Long Qian', 'Xue Feng', 'Zou Na') AND checking.type NOT LIKE '%red_packet%' AND customer.province LIKE '%Yunn%an%' GROUP BY customer.gender, company.last_update_timestamp, company.category ORDER BY customer.gender, company.last_update_timestamp, company.category;

SELECT transfer.fresh_ts, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(savingAccount.userID + customer.checking_credit) as agg_1, SUM(savingAccount.Isblocked) as agg_2 FROM savingAccount JOIN customer ON savingAccount.userID = customer.custID JOIN company ON customer.companyID = company.companyID JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.sourceID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.targetID JOIN checkingAccount ON customer.custID = checkingAccount.userID JOIN loantrans ON customer.custID = loantrans.applicantID JOIN loanapps ON loantrans.appID = loanapps.id  WHERE loantrans.delinquency >= 0.0 AND checking.id >= 354815.4870222335 AND loanapps.status IN ('under_review') AND checkingAccount.userID <= 208705.39477456996 AND customer.saving_credit >= 0.0 AND (company.saving_credit >= 0.0 OR (company.province IN ('Gansu', 'Jilin', 'Chongqing', 'Guangdong', 'Guangxi') AND company.saving_credit <= 0.0)) AND loantrans.loantrans_ts LIKE '%2023-10-21%' AND company.Isblocked >= 0.0 AND customer.name != 'Tang Pengfei' GROUP BY transfer.fresh_ts ORDER BY transfer.fresh_ts LIMIT 1000;

SELECT loanapps.status, company.name, SUM(loantrans.duration) as agg_0, MIN(customer.saving_credit + loantrans.id) as agg_1, AVG(transfer.sourceID + savingAccount.Isblocked) as agg_2 FROM savingAccount JOIN customer ON savingAccount.userID = customer.custID JOIN company ON customer.companyID = company.companyID JOIN transfer ON customer.custID = transfer.sourceID JOIN loantrans ON customer.custID = loantrans.applicantID JOIN loanapps ON loantrans.appID = loanapps.id JOIN checkingAccount ON customer.custID = checkingAccount.userID JOIN checking ON customer.custID = checking.sourceID  WHERE customer.province LIKE '%Hebei%' AND loanapps.status IN ('under_review', 'reject', 'accept') AND loantrans.applicantID >= 300811.84176411637 AND customer.city NOT LIKE '%Chongqing%' AND checking.targetID <= 224228.5644159921 AND (checking.amount >= 697.7419909650522 OR checking.amount <= 619.1227881562361) AND loanapps.id >= 272380.09500482003 AND customer.gender IN ('female', 'male') AND customer.loan_balance >= 10000.0 AND (transfer.type LIKE '%red_%packet%' OR transfer.type = 'business') AND loantrans.loantrans_ts NOT LIKE '%2023-11%-15%' AND company.Isblocked <= 0.0 AND transfer.amount <= 19.949384428439807 GROUP BY loanapps.status, company.name ORDER BY loanapps.status, company.name;

SELECT payment.payment_dt, member.lastname, AVG(member.region_no + region.region_no) as agg_0, MIN(payment.payment_no) as agg_1 FROM provider JOIN region ON provider.region_no = region.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE corporation.city = ' ' AND payment.payment_dt = '1999-09-02 00:00:00' AND corporation.street = ' ' AND provider.provider_no >= 246.34963471119679 AND payment.payment_no >= 2328.6204301072485 AND statement.due_dt != '1999-09-02 00:00:00' AND corporation.corp_name LIKE '%M%akersCorp.%' GROUP BY payment.payment_dt, member.lastname ORDER BY payment.payment_dt, member.lastname;

SELECT region.mail_code, member.mail_code, member.state_prov, AVG(provider.region_no) as agg_0, SUM(statement.statement_amt + member.region_no) as agg_1, AVG(provider.provider_no) as agg_2 FROM corporation JOIN region ON corporation.region_no = region.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE provider.provider_name IN ('Prov. Apex Mach', 'Prov. Expert Re', 'Prov. Boston Ne', 'Prov. Expert Sa', 'Prov. Boston Pe', 'Prov. Apex Key') AND corporation.expr_dt NOT LIKE '%20%04-10-12%' AND statement.due_dt LIKE '%1999-10-03%' AND payment.payment_amt <= 18238.75260494779 AND corporation.street != ' ' AND (member.issue_dt LIKE '%1999-10-13%' OR member.lastname LIKE '%UNAKLET%' OR member.issue_dt NOT LIKE '%1999-10-13%') AND region.street IN ('777 Seventh St', '333 Third St.', '222 Second St.', '555 Fifth St St', '111 First St.', '666 Sixth', '888 Eighth St.', '444 Fourth St.', '999 Ninth St.') AND statement.due_dt = '1999-10-03 00:00:00' AND member.city = ' ' AND payment.payment_dt LIKE '%1999-10-03%' AND (region.country = 'Sw' OR region.country = 'Ca' OR region.country != 'Ke') GROUP BY region.mail_code, member.mail_code, member.state_prov HAVING AVG(provider.region_no) >= 7.76 ORDER BY region.mail_code, member.mail_code, member.state_prov;

SELECT region.region_name, category.category_code, MIN(charge.member_no) as agg_0, MAX(provider.region_no + charge.charge_amt) as agg_1 FROM charge JOIN member ON charge.member_no = member.member_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE member.prev_balance <= 0.0 AND member.expr_dt LIKE '%2000-10-12%' AND (region.city = 'Brussels' OR region.city = 'Beijing') GROUP BY region.region_name, category.category_code ORDER BY region.region_name, category.category_code LIMIT 100;

SELECT statement.statement_dt, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(statement.statement_amt + charge.member_no) as agg_1, MIN(corporation.corp_no + charge.category_no) as agg_2 FROM category JOIN charge ON category.category_no = charge.category_no JOIN member ON charge.member_no = member.member_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no  WHERE (region.region_name != 'China' OR region.country != 'Ja') AND payment.payment_no >= 3699.2686513109447 AND statement.due_dt LIKE '%1999-%10-03%' AND (category.category_desc = 'Entertainment' OR (category.category_desc = 'Travel' AND category.category_desc = 'Communication')) AND payment.payment_dt NOT LIKE '%1999-10-03%' AND corporation.region_no <= 4.3405093147313165 AND provider.street = ' ' AND charge.charge_amt <= 2728.189898893866 AND statement.statement_dt LIKE '%1999-09-13%' GROUP BY statement.statement_dt ORDER BY statement.statement_dt;

SELECT MIN(charge.category_no) as agg_0, MIN(statement.statement_no + member.prev_balance) as agg_1 FROM region JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no  WHERE member.expr_dt IN ('2000-10-12 10:43:25', '2000-10-12 10:42:22', '2000-10-12 10:42:11', '2000-10-12 10:42:01', '2000-10-12 10:43:02', '2000-10-12 10:43:29', '2000-10-12 10:42:44', '2000-10-12 10:43:24', '2000-10-12 10:42:05') AND corporation.city != ' ' AND provider.city = ' ' AND payment.payment_dt LIKE '%00:00:00%' AND category.category_no <= 2.518358732427771 AND statement.statement_dt = '1999-08-13 00:00:00' AND region.street LIKE '%St.%' HAVING MIN(charge.category_no) != 5.99572;

SELECT member.lastname, region.street, member.photograph, SUM(charge.category_no + payment.statement_no) as agg_0 FROM category JOIN charge ON category.category_no = charge.category_no JOIN member ON charge.member_no = member.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no  WHERE corporation.corp_name NOT LIKE '%RestaurantsCo.%' AND charge.charge_no <= 74959.99536424584 AND statement.statement_dt = '1999-08-13 00:00:00' AND payment.payment_dt IN ('1999-10-03 00:00:00') AND member.expr_dt != '2000-10-12 10:41:56' AND provider.expr_dt LIKE '%10:41:%18%' AND member.firstname != 'PXTKITILQHFKRK' AND region.region_name IN ('North American', 'Eastern Europea', 'South American', 'China', 'Africa', 'Japan', 'Western Europea', 'Scandanavian') GROUP BY member.lastname, region.street, member.photograph ORDER BY member.lastname, region.street, member.photograph;

SELECT member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial, region.city, SUM(charge.statement_no) as agg_0, MIN(member.prev_balance) as agg_1, MAX(corporation.region_no) as agg_2 FROM corporation JOIN region ON corporation.region_no = region.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE provider.expr_dt NOT LIKE '%10:41%:22%' AND provider.region_no <= 8.0 AND member.lastname LIKE '%XAVIE%R%' AND corporation.city != ' ' AND member.expr_dt LIKE '%2000-10-12%' AND (statement.statement_amt <= 15330.551879176222 OR statement.due_dt != '1999-09-02 00:00:00' OR statement.statement_amt >= 21614.234256275035) GROUP BY member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial, region.city ORDER BY member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial, region.city;

SELECT corporation.city, corporation.state_prov, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(charge.category_no + region.region_no) as agg_1 FROM region JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no  WHERE region.region_name NOT LIKE '%American%' AND provider.expr_dt IN ('2000-10-12 10:41:23') AND category.category_no >= 9.430296411237808 AND (provider.city = ' ' OR provider.provider_name = 'Prov. Just Petr' OR provider.city = ' ') AND payment.payment_dt IN ('1999-09-02 00:00:00') AND region.city != 'Goteborg' AND provider.street = ' ' AND corporation.street = ' ' AND member.lastname LIKE '%NE%LSON%' AND (statement.due_dt LIKE '%199%9-09-02%' OR statement.due_dt != '1999-09-02 00:00:00') AND region.street IN ('999 Ninth St.', '666 Sixth', '555 Fifth St St') GROUP BY corporation.city, corporation.state_prov ORDER BY corporation.city, corporation.state_prov;

SELECT MIN(member.region_no + member.corp_no) as agg_0 FROM member JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no  WHERE member.curr_balance <= 0.0 AND (region.region_name NOT LIKE '%Eu%ropea%' OR region.state_prov != 'ON') HAVING MIN(member.region_no + member.corp_no) >= 347.0748778961385;

SELECT region.country, member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM corporation JOIN region ON corporation.region_no = region.region_no JOIN member ON region.region_no = member.region_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE (payment.payment_dt IN ('1999-10-03 00:00:00', '1999-09-02 00:00:00') OR payment.payment_dt != '1999-10-03 00:00:00' OR payment.payment_dt LIKE '%1999-10%-03%') AND provider.issue_dt LIKE '%10:41:2%3%' AND provider.city = ' ' AND member.expr_dt IN ('2000-10-12 10:42:42', '2000-10-12 10:43:18', '2000-10-12 10:43:22', '2000-10-12 10:42:58', '2000-10-12 10:41:49', '2000-10-12 10:43:20', '2000-10-12 10:43:07', '2000-10-12 10:43:16', '2000-10-12 10:42:30') AND charge.charge_amt <= 2281.0773927114888 AND payment.payment_amt >= 10652.04261211789 AND member.curr_balance >= 0.0 AND statement.statement_no >= 12998.428480926568 AND region.region_name NOT LIKE '%A%merican%' GROUP BY region.country, member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial ORDER BY region.country, member.expr_dt, member.middleinitial;

SELECT corporation.phone_no, provider.issue_dt, provider.mail_code, MAX(member.member_no + region.region_no) as agg_0 FROM member JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no  WHERE (provider.street = ' ' OR provider.street != ' ') AND provider.issue_dt LIKE '%10:41:1%8%' AND region.region_name IN ('China', 'Eastern Europea', 'Japan', 'North American', 'Western Europea', 'Africa', 'South American', 'Scandanavian', 'Mid East / Sout') AND payment.payment_dt NOT LIKE '%1999-09-02%' AND category.category_desc = 'Groceries' AND region.street NOT LIKE '%St%.%' AND (corporation.corp_name LIKE '%Needle%workAg.%' OR (corporation.region_no <= 7.37725816064752 AND corporation.corp_name LIKE '%PetroleumCorp.%')) AND (payment.payment_amt <= 14784.451282304513 OR (payment.payment_no >= 6282.3665363288965 AND payment.payment_amt >= 3003.281592714843)) AND statement.statement_dt LIKE '%1999-08-13%' GROUP BY corporation.phone_no, provider.issue_dt, provider.mail_code ORDER BY corporation.phone_no, provider.issue_dt, provider.mail_code;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, MAX(charge.category_no + member.prev_balance) as agg_2 FROM payment JOIN member ON payment.member_no = member.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no  WHERE payment.payment_no >= 14086.765089263823 AND charge.statement_no >= 2079.691563786073 AND payment.payment_dt = '1999-10-03 00:00:00' AND (member.expr_dt IN ('2000-10-12 10:41:39', '2000-10-12 10:42:15', '2000-10-12 10:42:01', '2000-10-12 10:42:27') OR member.expr_dt NOT LIKE '%2000-10-1%2%' OR member.expr_dt LIKE '%2000-10%-12%') AND (member.issue_dt = '1999-10-13 10:42:15' OR member.issue_dt != '1999-10-13 10:42:33' OR member.issue_dt IN ('1999-10-13 10:41:33')) AND charge.provider_no >= 298.46584094887015;

SELECT corporation.state_prov, AVG(charge.statement_no + payment.payment_no) as agg_0, MIN(charge.category_no + category.category_no) as agg_1, MIN(payment.payment_no) as agg_2 FROM category JOIN charge ON category.category_no = charge.category_no JOIN member ON charge.member_no = member.member_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no  WHERE (charge.charge_no <= 1497597.2757906744 OR charge.category_no <= 6.427211426010774) AND category.category_desc = 'Misc' AND region.country != 'Ke' AND (payment.statement_no >= 0.0 OR (payment.statement_no <= 0.0 AND payment.statement_no <= 0.0)) AND (payment.payment_dt LIKE '%19%99-10-03%' OR payment.member_no >= 7846.015087886736 OR payment.payment_dt IN ('1999-09-02 00:00:00')) AND region.street LIKE '%S%t%' AND member.lastname NOT LIKE '%V%ANN%' AND corporation.expr_dt != '2004-10-12 10:41:26' AND member.issue_dt IN ('1999-10-13 10:42:46', '1999-10-13 10:43:37', '1999-10-13 10:42:50', '1999-10-13 10:43:10', '1999-10-13 10:43:16', '1999-10-13 10:42:00', '1999-10-13 10:42:30') GROUP BY corporation.state_prov ORDER BY corporation.state_prov;

SELECT provider.provider_name, SUM(provider.provider_no) as agg_0, MIN(category.category_no) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM statement JOIN member ON statement.member_no = member.member_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no  WHERE region.street = '444 Fourth St.' AND corporation.expr_dt != '2004-10-12 10:41:26' AND statement.due_dt NOT LIKE '%00:00:00%' AND charge.member_no <= 9890.251680393003 AND member.lastname NOT LIKE '%YEONG%' AND provider.issue_dt NOT LIKE '%10:41:24%' AND (payment.statement_no >= 0.0 OR payment.statement_no <= 0.0 OR payment.statement_no <= 0.0) GROUP BY provider.provider_name ORDER BY provider.provider_name;

SELECT AVG(statement.statement_no + charge.member_no) as agg_0, SUM(charge.category_no) as agg_1 FROM member JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no  WHERE region.state_prov != 'ON' AND payment.payment_no >= 14907.68243788311 AND member.issue_dt != '1999-10-13 10:43:32' AND region.region_name IN ('Eastern Europea', 'Japan', 'Western Europea', 'China') AND (corporation.city = ' ' OR (corporation.corp_no <= 80.7387714690247 AND corporation.city != ' ')) AND statement.statement_amt >= 0.0 AND member.street = ' ' AND (payment.payment_dt != '1999-10-03 00:00:00' OR payment.payment_dt LIKE '%00:%00:00%' OR payment.payment_dt NOT LIKE '%1999-0%9-02%') AND statement.statement_dt LIKE '%1999-09-13%' AND corporation.street = ' ' AND (corporation.expr_dt LIKE '%2004-10-12%' OR corporation.expr_dt = '2004-10-12 10:41:26' OR corporation.expr_dt = '2004-10-12 10:41:26') LIMIT 10;

SELECT member.member_code, member.photograph, MAX(statement.statement_amt) as agg_0 FROM member JOIN region ON member.region_no = region.region_no JOIN statement ON member.member_no = statement.member_no JOIN charge ON member.member_no = charge.member_no JOIN provider ON region.region_no = provider.region_no JOIN payment ON member.member_no = payment.member_no JOIN category ON charge.category_no = category.category_no JOIN corporation ON region.region_no = corporation.region_no  WHERE statement.due_dt = '1999-10-03 00:00:00' AND member.issue_dt IN ('1999-10-13 10:43:30') AND statement.statement_dt = '1999-09-13 00:00:00' AND charge.charge_no <= 890701.7115763617 GROUP BY member.member_code, member.photograph ORDER BY member.member_code, member.photograph;

SELECT lineitem.l_commitdate, COUNT(*) as agg_0, MIN(partsupp.ps_partkey) as agg_1, MAX(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey  WHERE part.p_container != 'LG PACK' AND lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct LIKE '%RETURN%' AND part.p_partkey >= 9825217.9021782 AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%I%N%' OR (lineitem.l_shipdate != '1994-09-12' AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'COLLECT COD')) AND partsupp.ps_suppkey <= 538822.9261456741 AND part.p_type != 'ECONOMY POLISHED NICKEL' AND part.p_mfgr LIKE '%Manufa%cturer#3%' AND part.p_container LIKE '%BO%X%' AND lineitem.l_receiptdate = '1995-10-19' AND lineitem.l_returnflag = 'A' AND lineitem.l_discount <= 0.09650228835522123 AND partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 174.70385029008497 AND partsupp.ps_availqty <= 4573.170913703382 AND part.p_type LIKE '%POLISHED%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 10647914.703139722 GROUP BY lineitem.l_commitdate ORDER BY lineitem.l_commitdate;

SELECT part.p_container, part.p_mfgr, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM lineitem JOIN partsupp ON lineitem.l_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey AND lineitem.l_suppkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_supplycost <= 363.8332713867948 AND part.p_type IN ('LARGE ANODIZED TIN', 'ECONOMY BURNISHED NICKEL', 'PROMO BRUSHED BRASS', 'STANDARD BRUSHED BRASS', 'LARGE ANODIZED COPPER', 'SMALL PLATED TIN', 'LARGE BRUSHED BRASS', 'STANDARD BURNISHED BRASS') AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 24609.692266638922 AND (orders.o_orderdate = '1998-06-19' OR (orders.o_orderdate != '1997-12-13' AND orders.o_orderdate = '1995-03-15')) AND orders.o_orderpriority != '4-NOT SPECIFIED' AND (partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 720503.192928958 OR partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 521893.5353978793) AND (lineitem.l_linestatus = 'O' OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('F', 'O') OR lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O', 'F')) AND orders.o_orderkey >= 70557452.76319848 AND part.p_container NOT LIKE '%WRAP%' AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 7736.599490030978 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'TAKE BACK RETURN' AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%furio%usly.%' AND lineitem.l_suppkey <= 725818.8936058718 AND orders.o_shippriority <= 0.0 AND part.p_partkey >= 9803895.167484423 AND lineitem.l_linenumber <= 3.0 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%have%' AND partsupp.ps_partkey <= 17756719.07631371 AND part.p_retailprice >= 2000.8243935464855 GROUP BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_container, part.p_mfgr;

SELECT lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority, AVG(lineitem.l_quantity + orders.o_totalprice) as agg_0, AVG(lineitem.l_tax) as agg_1, MIN(lineitem.l_linenumber) as agg_2 FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey  WHERE lineitem.l_shipmode NOT LIKE '%FOB%' AND orders.o_orderstatus != 'F' AND orders.o_totalprice >= 148685.19976339984 AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct NOT LIKE '%NONE%' AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.055662385420312814 AND lineitem.l_suppkey >= 976461.2275703691 AND (orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%4-NOT%' OR (orders.o_orderpriority LIKE '%1-URGENT%' AND orders.o_orderpriority NOT LIKE '%4-NO%T%')) AND orders.o_orderdate = '1995-12-17' AND (lineitem.l_partkey <= 18322815.410028506 OR (lineitem.l_quantity >= 49.1391161901332 AND lineitem.l_partkey <= 11438131.9831857)) AND lineitem.l_shipinstruct IN ('COLLECT COD') AND (orders.o_orderpriority = '3-MEDIUM' OR orders.o_custkey <= 11671494.246971939) AND (lineitem.l_linestatus != 'F' OR lineitem.l_returnflag = 'N') AND orders.o_comment LIKE '%sl%y%' AND orders.o_orderstatus = 'O' GROUP BY lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority HAVING AVG(lineitem.l_quantity + orders.o_totalprice) <= 151146.62272065197 ORDER BY lineitem.l_shipinstruct, orders.o_orderpriority;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, MAX(lineitem.l_partkey + lineitem.l_extendedprice) as agg_1 FROM partsupp JOIN part ON partsupp.ps_partkey = part.p_partkey JOIN lineitem ON partsupp.ps_partkey = lineitem.l_partkey AND partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_suppkey  WHERE lineitem.l_returnflag IN ('N') AND part.p_brand != 'Brand#34' AND part.p_size >= 19.09941297560922 AND partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%re%gular,%' AND lineitem.l_linenumber <= 1.0 AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 437947.38694172655 AND part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%Brand#2%3%' AND part.p_type = 'LARGE PLATED TIN' AND (lineitem.l_shipmode = 'MAIL' OR lineitem.l_comment NOT LIKE '%f%luffily%') AND lineitem.l_linestatus IN ('O') AND (lineitem.l_shipinstruct != 'DELIVER IN PERSON' OR lineitem.l_comment LIKE '%final%' OR lineitem.l_shipinstruct = 'DELIVER IN PERSON') AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 3649250.013419387 AND lineitem.l_shipdate = '1992-02-21' AND lineitem.l_tax >= 0.07791032737564735 AND lineitem.l_extendedprice >= 11957.202063119035;

SELECT part.p_mfgr, MIN(partsupp.ps_supplycost) as agg_0, MIN(partsupp.ps_availqty) as agg_1, AVG(partsupp.ps_suppkey + part.p_partkey) as agg_2 FROM part JOIN partsupp ON part.p_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey  WHERE partsupp.ps_comment LIKE '%packages%' AND part.p_container IN ('MED CAN', 'JUMBO CAN', 'LG PACK', 'JUMBO BOX', 'MED DRUM', 'LG BAG', 'LG PKG', 'MED PKG', 'WRAP CASE', 'MED BAG') AND part.p_name LIKE '%magen%ta%' AND part.p_container != 'LG CASE' AND partsupp.ps_suppkey >= 672734.2593798533 AND partsupp.ps_partkey >= 4549465.737915334 AND part.p_brand LIKE '%Brand#51%' AND part.p_type LIKE '%TIN%' AND (partsupp.ps_availqty <= 1566.2675258532172 OR (partsupp.ps_availqty <= 878.5037907799647 AND partsupp.ps_availqty >= 8674.808684152069)) AND (part.p_mfgr = 'Manufacturer#4' OR (part.p_size <= 41.926214118000914 AND part.p_mfgr IN ('Manufacturer#4', 'Manufacturer#1'))) AND part.p_retailprice >= 1673.602091274385 AND part.p_comment LIKE '%sly%ly%' AND part.p_type NOT LIKE '%ECONOMY%' AND (part.p_brand NOT LIKE '%Brand#2%3%' OR part.p_partkey <= 8653019.280937083) AND part.p_mfgr NOT LIKE '%Manufa%cturer#3%' GROUP BY part.p_mfgr ORDER BY part.p_mfgr;

SELECT item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id, MIN(web_sales.ws_ext_ship_cost) as agg_0, MIN(web_sales.ws_web_page_sk + web_page.wp_char_count) as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM web_page JOIN web_sales ON web_page.wp_web_page_sk = web_sales.ws_web_page_sk JOIN item ON web_sales.ws_item_sk = item.i_item_sk  WHERE item.i_manufact_id >= 160.0663267518406 AND web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y', 'N') AND (web_page.wp_web_page_id = 'AAAAAAAANJAAAAAA' OR (web_page.wp_type = 'feedback' AND web_page.wp_web_page_id = 'AAAAAAAAMFAAAAAA')) AND web_sales.ws_quantity <= 59.57187766462889 AND (web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y', 'N') OR (web_page.wp_autogen_flag IN ('Y') AND web_page.wp_autogen_flag IS NOT NULL)) AND item.i_manufact NOT LIKE '%stn%' AND item.i_current_price <= 3.7182270825488595 AND item.i_rec_end_date NOT LIKE '%2000-10-26%' AND item.i_color = 'indian' AND web_page.wp_url = 'http://www.foo.com' GROUP BY item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id ORDER BY item.i_color, item.i_units, web_page.wp_web_page_id;

SELECT time_dim.t_shift, COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM time_dim JOIN catalog_sales ON time_dim.t_time_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_time_sk  WHERE catalog_sales.cs_ext_ship_cost <= 352.52349340469453 AND catalog_sales.cs_ext_wholesale_cost <= 2204.796471481882 AND catalog_sales.cs_net_paid_inc_tax >= 218.9209264764219 AND (time_dim.t_meal_time LIKE '%lunc%h%' OR time_dim.t_meal_time NOT LIKE '%lunch%' OR time_dim.t_meal_time NOT LIKE '%breakfast%') AND catalog_sales.cs_ship_customer_sk <= 421974.7344066446 GROUP BY time_dim.t_shift ORDER BY time_dim.t_shift;

SELECT date_dim.d_current_week, item.i_manufact, COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM web_site JOIN date_dim ON web_site.web_close_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN inventory ON date_dim.d_date_sk = inventory.inv_date_sk JOIN store_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk JOIN item ON inventory.inv_item_sk = item.i_item_sk JOIN household_demographics ON store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON item.i_item_sk = catalog_returns.cr_item_sk JOIN time_dim ON catalog_returns.cr_returned_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN promotion ON store_sales.ss_promo_sk = promotion.p_promo_sk JOIN customer_address ON catalog_returns.cr_returning_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN ship_mode ON catalog_returns.cr_ship_mode_sk = ship_mode.sm_ship_mode_sk  WHERE inventory.inv_warehouse_sk >= 1.0773580725393934 AND (promotion.p_channel_catalog != 'N' OR (promotion.p_channel_catalog = 'N' AND promotion.p_channel_catalog != 'N')) AND web_site.web_open_date_sk >= 2450598.41327213 AND promotion.p_channel_press IS NOT NULL AND household_demographics.hd_demo_sk <= 5152.477478883706 AND time_dim.t_time_sk <= 56352.24992659456 AND promotion.p_channel_event IS NOT NULL AND store_sales.ss_store_sk <= 90.26043395686901 AND ship_mode.sm_code NOT LIKE '%SURFAC%E%' AND customer_address.ca_zip != '31409' AND store_sales.ss_item_sk >= 8587.795959861736 GROUP BY date_dim.d_current_week, item.i_manufact ORDER BY date_dim.d_current_week, item.i_manufact;
